<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Junk Food | Josh Vince</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <%= favicon_link_tag asset_path("favicon-32x32.png") %>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Libre+Franklin:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "tailwind", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "junk_food/junk_food", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "emoji_spray" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "junk_food_intro" %>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-bauhaus-cream text-bauhaus-black">
    <div class="intro-container">
      <div id="emoji-canvas" class="emoji-canvas"></div>

      <div class="intro-text px-6">
        <p class="font-junk text-2xl">The</p>
        <h1 class="font-junk text-7xl md:text-9xl leading-none mb-4">Junk Food<br>Firehose</h1>
        <button id="open-wide" class="is-invisible bauhaus-btn mt-6 px-10 py-3 bg-bauhaus-red text-white text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-3 border-bauhaus-black">Open wide</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="intro-content" class="is-hidden is-invisible font-junk-body px-6 py-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg">
        Many modern foods are harmful to us if we consume them in extreme quantities. Most people exercise some kind of moderation
        with the fuel they put into their bodies.
        Statistically, you're not a chain-smoker or a functioning alcoholic or someone who consumes kilos of chocolate every day.
        Cigarettes and alcohol and chocolate bars come with warning labels.
        <br/><br/>
        But content comes with no warnings. Most of us pretty much constantly consume content throughout our
        waking hours, drinking directly from a firehose that squirts unmoderated streams of it from the internet to our pocket
        straight into our brains.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg">
        Complete abstention is only for a tiny fraction. The rest of us have to get by with being thoughtful
        with what we consume.
        <br/><br/>
        Our information diet deserves warning labels as well.
      </p>
      <%= form_with url: junk_food_path, method: :post, class: "w-full flex flex-col justify-center space-y-5" do |f| %>
        <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">What was the last piece of content you consumed?</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          name="name"
          id="name"
          required
          placeholder="eg: an article about Epstein"
          minLength="3"
          maxLength="35"
          autocomplete="off"
          class="w-full px-4 py-3 border-3 border-bauhaus-black text-lg bg-white focus:outline-none focus:border-bauhaus-blue"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="block bauhaus-btn mt-6 px-10 py-3 bg-bauhaus-red text-white text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-3 border-bauhaus-black"
        >
          Make a label
        </button>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
